item.title: CVE-2017-16124|2024-09-16T18:19:41.237Z -- hackerone -- node-server-forfront%20node%20module
item.description: node-server-forfront is a simple static file server. node-server-forfront is vulnerable to a directory traversal issue, giving an attacker access to the filesystem by placing "../" in the url.
